Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, the powers of darkness are embracing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels very nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte Wreckmeister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall grant...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can wander about in limbo with your loved one for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hand over any more fragments to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill the owner of the Aeon's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't kill him!{asa: changed}{err avaritia was talking to superbia, so shiori was referring to her}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{kono go ni yoreba aiirenai}Do you really think you can defeat me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{kiru ka}Will you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten about my immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without enough fragments, the only thing that can grant your desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this right eye of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, there's only one way to save Yuka... everyone... the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
