Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri-neesan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And so, they both lived happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dull!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! {lol...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, something did happen! What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun! Let's go to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's read a book in your room then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, they're ruined. I'll go get some more, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for you... I always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you stabbed yourself in the throat with Raikiri, Yuka used her powers to make Raikiri disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liselotte temporarily lost her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave Shiori and I a small opening in order to carry you and Yuka here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fatigued from using her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also probably from the shock as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, you are an utter fool for trying to take your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And so, they both lived happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I{'d} understood, but apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to live. No matter the cost, I have to stay by Yuka's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm still alive, I need to repay her for everything she's ever done for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...plus interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, I have to defeat Liselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends and for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"While I'm still alive", huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you just an illusion that Yuka made?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Kukuri-san is different to the one in Yuka-san's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Abraxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit that resided in your sister's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit in her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to seek vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master, Satsuki Kukuri, took her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought that without the necessary number of fragments, Liselotte would be unable to perform the Descent to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew about the Descent to Hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she killed her little brother, the holder of the Aeon's Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then... Why is Kakeru alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abraxus killed Kakeru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Kakeru-san did not possess the Aeon's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kakeru-san who did possess it was in a world different from Kukuri's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka's world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is why you are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:11:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither a fragment nor Abraxus resided in the body of the Kukuri-san that was in Yuka-san's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she simply just took her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I lost you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two different Kukuri-sans in two different worlds both knew about the Decent to Hell, and both took the same course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kukuri-san who possessed a fragment used Abraxus to kill Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuka's world's Kukuri-san didn't have Abraxus, so she couldn't kill Kakeru with her own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This living Kakeru is you, and you were the sole owner of the Aeon's Eye all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you were originally with the Kukuri-san that did possess a fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, due to some development, Yuka-san used her fragment's power to call you over to her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subconsciously, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the one Kukuri-san talked to was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:12:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked about the truth with Kukuri-san in not just two worlds, but six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not figure out just which world's Kukuri-san possessed the fragment, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can traverse space-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you only tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time that I received my orders, only Kukuri-san was old enough to understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you told my sister to die in order to protect the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did not. All I did was warn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not think she would actually do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gravely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I believe that intervention was the worst action I could have taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not in the Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The master of this world is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's sealed Yuka-san's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've no more intention of taking your own life, Satsuki Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Yuka back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you come here, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The black moon is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us all succumb to the Descent to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe that the black knights will have a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is. Only her {editor choose}heart{/soul} was not artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-san's fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is betting everything on you by giving that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that, you may be able to seal off Liselotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori possessed the power to traverse space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you combine her powers with the Aeon's Eye, you may be able to seal Liselotte away in a dimensional rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is certainly worth trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save Kakeru? Weren't you trying to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chances of saving this world are now close to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there is nothing left to be done but believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot afford to be arguing. Avaritia-sama's seal on her is growing weaker by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting is my job. I will protect you, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{kagi kake tozasu soukou no mon}The sealed gate of enlightenment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{shichiwaku shichisei ga manekitaru, yurai soufu no sei}The heavenly bodies seven, instilling power upon Gaea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{mugoku rei rei, isogite ritsuryou no gotoku nase}Ye shalt chant naught the hymn of war, but swiftly mine will consummate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{chitose no tomogara}Wielding the power of one thousand generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{shinuchi doujigiri yasutsuna}Shinuchi Doujigiri Yasutsuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真打 童子切　安綱: "True Blade" \N{\i1}Child Killer{\i0}, forged by blacksmith Yasutsuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life-devouring sword, Doujigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become your shield, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You love him as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, a human's heart is what determines whether to destroy or protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope is nothing more than a fleeting dream that you will wake to despair from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I'd figured out my mistake... \NJust when I'd decided on changing myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to take away our tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not give up, no matter who says otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not believe that there's only despair waiting for us after that "fleeting dream"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good things and bad things may be in store for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends and enemies may be lying in wait for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something bad, then just do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give up, then that's just going to be the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such childish banter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! My words might sound like nonsense to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what I think! I believe that our tomorrow will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was alone... and I was prepared to live accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true. I've been supported by everyone all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka was there for me. I was able to remain sane because she was at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect our world... our tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liselotte.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thought from the Aeon's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not take away these children's future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verard... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was wrong. I was not truly looking at the hearts of men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This boy showed me the light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please understand, Liselotte. You must not destroy this world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{翠玉碑の一片}What my eight hundred years of solitude desires is a piece of the Emerald Tablet, the Aeon's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Emerald Tablet: An ancient text purporting to reveal the secret of {\i1}ylem{\i0} (primordial substance) and its transmutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Focus, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Douji, O Douji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devour mine flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver unto the great evil a demon's sacred flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kigazettou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鬼牙絶刀: Demon Fang Executioner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall unto eternal slumber, Witch of Babylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avaritia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With its master gone, the Crimson Night can no longer remain stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I will transport you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a future like this actually existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'll entrust the Kusakabe {editor pick}household to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kakeru! You're trying to keep Yuka-rin all to yourself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good! Let me join in on the fun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go spouting off nonsense! Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not a word about the Crimson Night was spoken between Yuka and I ever since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I opened that tumbling doll, \Nthere was a smaller tumbling doll inside of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened that small doll, an even smaller one was in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You grabbed some cash again from my wallet, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takahisa-senpai! I wasn't done talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay with your body, you runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only 150 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukiko and Takahisa didn't know either of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kukuri-neesan and Shiori-san are also absent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.51,0:24:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.42,0:24:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to Ayanas. Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know whose world this is. All I know is that it's peaceful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.34,0:24:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nice out, eh? {weather, or at least "outside"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Ah, yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that isn't the future...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...then this world will have a tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:54.93,11eyes - TS,,0095,0000,0087,,{\an7\fs96\c&H000000&\fnGeorgia\fscx90}Will you come tomorrow?
